data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after gated community of Old School House at Arborwalk! This exceptionally rare single-story residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and luxury with its impressive features.    Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the stunning upgraded tile flooring that sets the tone for the entire 1740 sq. ft. of open living space. There is a  formal living and dining room providing an elegant and inviting atmosphere.    The heart of this home is its upgraded kitchen that seamlessly opens to the family room, featuring a stone-finished fireplace for cozy gatherings. Ideal for entertaining, the kitchen is a chef's delight with granite countertops, a center island, ample storage, and a dedicated workspace for the kids to conquer their homework after school.    Step through the kitchen and discover a generously sized backyard, perfect for your future pool, with stamped concrete and a freshly painted covered patio – an ideal setting for summer BBQs and outdoor enjoyment.    The master retreat is a spacious haven that opens up to the backyard, offering a private escape. Three additional bedrooms provide versatility and ample space for family and guests. The convenience of an inside laundry adds to the practicality of this charming abode.    Car enthusiasts and DIY enthusiasts alike will appreciate the attached 3-car garage, complete with a built-in workbench and epoxy flooring. Additional noteworthy features include newer carpet throughout and an upgraded AC system, ensuring comfort year-round.    Situated in the award-winning Murrieta Valley Unified School District and conveniently close to shopping amenities, this home is not just a residence; it's an opportunity to own a gem in Murrieta. The meticulous care and thoughtful upgrades make this home move-in ready.  Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
